CommonEvent 6
Name = "EV006"

  Page 0
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["Donate 2000 Choco-Dicks for +1 Wealth to this"])
    ShowText(["reign?"])
    ShowChoices([["Yes", "No"], 2])
    When([0, "Yes"])
      ConditionalBranch([1, 584, 0, 2000, 1])
        ControlVariables([585, 585, 0, 0, -2000])
        ControlSwitches([648, 648, 0])
        PlaySE(["RPG::SE(@name=\"Coin\", @pitch=100, @volume=100)"])
        ControlVariables([387, 387, 1, 0, 1])
        Wait([45])
        Empty([])
      Else([])
        ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
        ShowText(["You don't have enough Choco-Dicks!"])
        Empty([])
      BranchEnd([])
      Empty([])

    When([1, "No"])
      Empty([])

    ChoicesEnd([])
    Empty([])
